div.span:
Well, there's plenty of applications. For one, what if I
need to hide in case of an emergency? And two, what if I
want to be delivered to someone's mailbox? I'll bet you wish
you could hypothetically be delivered to someone's mailbox.

div.span:
Ikabod! My real name is Ikabod--well, at least that's what
my parents called me. But somehow, they messed up when
writing it down! So formally I'm Ik.

Wait, did you just shout a random number? Sir, I hope you're
really paying attention. Our friendship is what's on the
line, after all.

Oh, by the way, don't worry about the Mother Slug. It's
securely contained beneath floor 295. We have security
systems in place.

It's so lousy. Explore as much as you can, but if there's
ever so much as a corner of the room in shadow, you're lost.

That's why I built the Upturned Inn! It's a loophole I
found, you see? You may be lost in the Afterlife, but you
always know where you are when you're in the good old
Upturned.

front desk, but it's black, so it blends in like a

like to stuff my whole body into shoeboxes on a regular
basis.

Question 1! Sir, Ik is my business moniker. But what is my
real name? Can you remember?

TWO days. Yes, that's right. I'm sick! I'm a daredevil!

fashion statement.
